{
  "stem": "8916.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I always-- the whole time that I was in this situation, I tried to associate myself with adults.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Again, it was just instinct.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was not just being that smart.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I knew-- plus I knew that I could figure out that they don't value adults, able-bodied adults, why would they worry about children?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I knew that even then.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as it turned out, they took all those children out and murdered them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- there was one incident where those children were all gathered up, all the barracks and taken away in trucks and never seen again.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was-- by that time I was already in Schindler's company.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was taken to Krakow where the-- where the Schindler's company was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Emalia.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I worked for Schindler until the company had to be dismantled because the Russians were invading in back.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the front where the Germans was going very badly.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the Russians were going to be in Krakow soon.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So companies like Schindler's company were just dismantle their company and let their-- their prisoners go back to Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, we did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I used to work night shift mostly. 12 hour shifts, standing near a machine and doing labor work.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I encountered Schindler many times as he was walking through the company.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes, he did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a-- there was a-- somehow-- some kind of a special relationship between Schindler and my father.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As you know, Schindler was not an angel in dealing with black-marketeering.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was a womanizer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he didn't mind taking bribes and giving bribes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he was not your squeaky clean kind of character.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
